## Why v348 Works
1. AdaptiveV3 base: conservative economy-gated budgets prevent crash
2. Team-size cap: guarantees miners in sub-team when sharing with partner
3. Idle scramble at min_res>=14: aggressive scrambling against weak opponents
4. No dedicated scramblers in budget: hearts saved for aligners

## Key Tournament Insights
- Conservative budgets >> aggressive in tournament (economy sustainability)
- Idle scrambling >> dedicated scramblers (flexible, economy-aware)
- Team cap helps on AdaptiveV3 base (modest cap on already-conservative budgets)
- Team cap HURTS on Aggressive base (removes too many aligners)

